data.description: Moody home with great Location at the end of Cul de Sac. Quaint front porch with low maintenance vinyl siding surround the home. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and just over 1,480 SF there's a lot to love here! In the living room you'll find creek rock fireplace with gas starter and Built-in Bookshelves. Create a show piece library for you or the kids! STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES make theme in so much easier! Covered deck with screened back porch for year round enjoyment. Offering a 1 car garage for easy unloading of grocery or during a rain storm you'll love the convenience! Local to all shopping, restaurants, and recreation this Moody home is prime location to call your next home!
